497
00:31:27,130 --> 00:31:29,830
Banxia sudah memberitahuku mengenai hal itu kemarin.

498
00:31:36,470 --> 00:31:39,139
Jangan khawatir, Menteri Han.

499
00:31:39,139 --> 00:31:42,080
Kau baik-baik saja.

500
00:31:44,600 --> 00:31:46,200
Terima kasih.

501
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:48,729
Tabib Zhang, kau memiliki jiwa dan hati yang berbudi.

502
00:31:48,730 --> 00:31:50,980
